Habang hindi pa namin natitiyak kung paa.source_string: While we don't know for sure that this virus will behave the same way as SARS-CoV and MERS-CoV, we can use the information gained from both of these earlier coronaviruses to guide us. In general, because of poor survivability of these coronaviruses on surfaces, there is likely very low risk of spread from products or packaging that are shipped over a period of days or weeks at ambient temperatures. Coronaviruses are generally thought to be spread most often by respiratory droplets. Currently there is no evidence to support transmission of COVID-19 associated with imported goods and there have not been any cases of COVID-19 in the United States associated with imported goods. Information will be provided on the Coronavirus Disease 2019 (COVID-19) website as it becomes available.

In {%1=app name}'s Premier Merchant Program, merchant performance across a variety of metrics is tracked in an automated way, and if it meets or exceeds certain thresholds, merchants are eligible for the Premier badge. User ratings of the merchant and the merchant's items, refunds, fulfillment, and compliance with {%1=app name} policies are some of the more notable groups of elements that are tracked. When {%1=app name} shows the badge and a brief description, we may highlight a few areas that reflect merchant performance in specific categories such as item quality, fulfillment & shipping, and customer satisfaction. The formula or approach for monitoring and reporting on merchant performance, including performance areas and minimum scores, may be updated over time.

At Wish, we put customers first and are willing to pay to insure that Wish users receive excellent service. Today, we learned that one of your orders was not prepared in accordance with Postnord rules, so we have automatically refunded you for your purchase!

Sometimes, merchants have already shipped your package. If this is the case, you may receive a message from Postnord to pay VAT and the handling fee. Since you have already been refunded, you will have two options:

1. If you don't want your item, then do nothing & ignore the messages. OR.
2. If you do want your item, contact Postnord with your order ID and they will release the package free of charge. That means we‚Äôve covered your whole purchase, shipping fees & Postnord VAT for you!

We apologize for any inconvenience and are working round the clock to make sure all 1 million merchants follow Postnord rules in the future!
